  production this color revival of the munsters starred john schuck ( as herman ) , lee meriwether ( lily ) , howard morton ( grandpa ) , hilary van dyke ( marilyn ) and jason marsden ( eddie ) , and broadcast 72 episodes from october 8 , 1988 , to may 25 , 1991 , giving it more first - run episodes than the original series .

